title: Ralph Breaks The Internet: Wreck-It Ralph 2 -  Hidden Easter Eggs

json.text: Get ready for Ralph Breaks the Internet!

Wreck it Ralph 2 is going to be jam packed
with awesome pop culture references and we've

already seen a bunch in the new trailer and
we can guarantee you probably missed them

the first time around, so we are here to help
you out and find some easter eggs!

Let's dive in and see what we found in Wreck
It Ralph 2

First up is Mr Litwak's arcade, inside his
office you can see in the background theres

two decorative plates featuring master yoda
and chewie!

Now this one might be a stretch but I am pretty
sure Mr Litwaks computer has a hidden mickey
as the logo, or maybe that's stitch?

One scene takes place at Ebay where Ralph
and vanelope stumble across a cat painting

for sale but if you look closely there are
some familiar items for sale in the background.

There is the magic lamp from Aladdin, and
a frying pan from Tangled...

We've seen a lot of comments about this little
girl in the trailer who looks a lot like baby

moana, heres a comparison of the two, what
do you think?
Leave your comment down below.

Could this be a little shoutout to Moana,
If you watched the end credits of Moana you
can see some Ralph art!

There are so many brands hidden in the movie
here are some that we found, like cisco, hulu,

mashable, youtube red, a hilarious poop emoji
game called down stream, trip advisor, imdb,

and there are some fake sites out there like
buzzfood and national seographic.

This is just the teaser trailer and we've
found so much, I can't wait to see what we
find when the full trailer comes out.

Wreck It Ralph 2 loads into theaters this
Thanksgiving and I can't wait!
